Notes for dataset users:

The visa matrix generated by this tool is based on publicly-available
information from official government sources. It is provided "as-is" with
no warranty of accuracy or completeness. Visa rules change without notice.
Always verify with the relevant embassy or consulate before making travel
or immigration decisions based on this data.
